  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cartographie des risques de\ncorruption<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Compte-rendu d’entretien<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"186\" style=\"width:139.5pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Élément</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"481\" style=\"width:360.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Donnée</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"186\" style=\"width:139.5pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date\n  de l’interview</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"481\" style=\"width:360.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2 mars 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"186\" style=\"width:139.5pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Personne\n  interviewée</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"481\" style=\"width:360.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Magali BURCKART<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"186\" style=\"width:139.5pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Fonction</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"481\" style=\"width:360.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Responsable Talent Acquisition\n  &amp; Marque Employeur<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"186\" style=\"width:139.5pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"481\" style=\"width:360.6pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Antoine LASSAUGE, Sandra LASAGNI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0\">1. Périmètre de\nresponsabilités et activités<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Fonction</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"> : Responsable Talent Acquisition &amp; Marque Employeur\n     – fonction groupe rattachée à la DRH<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Taille &amp; organisation de l’équipe</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Responsabilité directe de l’équipe\n      centrale (La Défense).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Supervision fonctionnelle des recruteurs\n      sur sites français : Arras (2), Lille (1), Ulis/Alès (1).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Animation métier élargie d’une\n      communauté France + filiales.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Périmètre géographique</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">France + filiales DOI : UK,\n      Belgique, Allemagne, Espagne et Mexique.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Missions principales</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Pilotage des recrutements</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> via indicateurs (taux d’adhérence\n      au plan de recrutement, délais de recrutement, taux de rupture de périodes\n      d’essai, etc.).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Déploiement de programmes RH </span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">: marque employeur, cooptation,\n      politique stages &amp; alternance.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Gestion des cabinets de\n      recrutement</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">\n      (relations + budget + accords commerciaux).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Conduite directe des\n      recrutements sensibles ou stratégiques</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n      11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> (postes COMEX et leadership team).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Support opérationnel global\n      pour les filiales</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%\"> suivant le périmètre Talent Acquisition.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Processus de recrutement&nbsp;:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Processus porté par <b>Workday</b>,\n      depuis la demande de poste jusqu’à la lettre d’engagement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Workflow différent selon qu’il\n      s’agit d’un poste <b>budgeté</b> (validation N+1, contrôle de gestion,\n      HRBP et TA) ou <b>hors budget</b> (validation COMEX). Étapes obligatoires\n      : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">cadrage du besoin avec le\n       manager,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">rédaction et publication de\n       l’offre,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">screening et tri des CVs par\n       l’équipe TA,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">entretiens croisés TA/manager,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">utilisation d’outils\n       psychométriques,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">validation N+2,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">prise de références (groupe 7+),<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">validation salariale via HRBP\n       ou Comp&amp;Ben,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">contractualisation par les Opérations\n       RH.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l7 level2 lfo1;\ntab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">o<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Cas particuliers<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Possibilité de non‑publication\n       d’une offre pour raisons de confidentialité, validée conjointement par\n       HRBP / DRH / Virginie Scanu.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Dans certaines filiales,\n       notamment <b>Mexique</b>, il arrive que les recrutements ne soient pas\n       immédiatement formalisés dans Workday et soient formalisés qu’à la\n       dernière étape (formation des équipes locales).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Gestion particulière des\n       intérimaires par les équipes RH locales (hors périmètre TA sauf\n       exceptions).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0\">2. Tiers et risques\nassociés<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.1. Managers internes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:\nlist 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\n11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Champ d’action :</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Initiateurs des demandes de\n      recrutement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Participation systématique aux\n      entretiens.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Possibilité de solliciter des\n      créations de poste ou des recrutements non planifiés.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cas rares de demande de non‑publication\n      d’offre.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:\nlist 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\n11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Risques :</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Favoritisme / conflit\n      d’intérêts (pression pour recruter un candidat connu).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Influence indue dans les\n      recrutements stratégiques.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Utilisation opportuniste du\n      hors budget pour accélérer un recrutement identifié.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Abus de la confidentialité pour\n      réserver un poste (annonce non publiée)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:\nlist 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\n11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Contrôles existants :</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Workflow Workday (validation\n      N+1, contrôle de gestion, HRBP, TA).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Validation systématique par le\n      N+2 pour décision finale.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Processus d’entretien croisé\n      (manager + recruteur).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Utilisation d’outils\n      psychométriques.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Décision collégiale pour les\n      cas de non-publication.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Revue critique des demandes\n      2026 dans un contexte financier renforcé.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.2. HRBP / DRH / Direction<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:\nlist 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\n11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Champ d’action :</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Validation des demandes de\n      recrutement.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Décision finale pour les\n      demandes exceptionnelles ou sensibles.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Pilotage de l’application des\n      politiques (télétravail, rémunération, avantages).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:\nlist 36.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\n11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%\">Risques :</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Favoritisme ou influence locale\n      excessive dans les recrutements stratégiques.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Validation complaisante de\n      non-publication d’offres.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Attribution d’un package\n      salaire et avantages en nature hors standards.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n